'''Myōhō Hakase''' (明法博士, みょうほうはかせ) was an [[official]] belonging to the {{ill|Daigakuryō|ja|大学寮|1=Daigaku-ryō|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Daigakuryō|13=User:Immanuelle/Daigaku-ryō|qq=}} under the {{ill|Ritsuryō system|ja|律令制|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ritsuryō system|qq=}} in ancient Japan. It was an {{ill|Extraordinary Office|ja|令外官|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Extraordinary Office|qq=}} with two positions. Initially, it was Ranked as ''Shōshichii-ge'' (正七位下). Later, it came to be filled by members of prestigious families.

